{"tid":1745472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《國際線課金！告上聯合國！》Human Rights Foundation香港專案","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T03:35:58.000Z","uid":116497,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"25ea4204751aae7def353045a850684ee7e713be","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位良心金主，有班手足飛到去美國搵到人權基金Human Rights Foundation合作，設立一個為期一年嘅Hong Kong Desk香港專案小組，跪求課金支持！</span></span></strong><br />\n官方網頁：<a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1396191c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\n直接捐款：<a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f5ec1ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> （捐款單位係美金，用呢條link，官網右上個掣係全球一般捐款）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Human Rights Foundation係乜水？</strong></span><br />\n</span>網站：<a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=6c9aa54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://HRF.org</a><br />\n一個喺紐約嘅人權組織，專門對抗全球暴政。最出名嘅活動係Oslo Freedom Forum (OFF)，年年請暴政下嘅各國代表做講者，何韻詩都去過三次！經濟學人曾經講過OFF就係世界經濟論壇嘅人權版。仲有，藍絲一路話呢個就係所謂「暴徒培訓」，敵人反對的，就應該要支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個Hong Kong Desk會做乜？</strong></span><br />\n</span>1. 主要任務係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寫信去6個聯合國旗下嘅自由/人權委員會</span></span></strong>，迫港共中共政府向聯合國<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回應問題</span></span></strong>，將佢哋嘅人權侵犯大力<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推上國際層面</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 喺各大<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際傳媒出文章繼續保持香港曝光率</span></span></strong>。個組織一定企喺雞蛋嘅一邊，寫嘅文章立場可以放心，而且唔用廣告直接借佢哋media team用op-ed形式出文，慳返啲登報錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 積極游說<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制裁人權侵犯者</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">要籌幾多？</span></span></strong><br />\n目標係19.5萬美金（約150萬港幣）<br />\n香港人登報一日都籌到幾百萬啦，個專案諗住做一年，係一年咁長㗎！仲唔快快手支持下？即去 <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f5ec1ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> 直接捐俾呢個project！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">仲有其他問題？</span></span></strong><br />\n睇呢度 《常見問題FAQ》 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/37snDcD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37snDcD&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=19a549a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37snDcD</a><br />\n<br />\n請follow<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=6c9aa54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://HRF.org</a><br />\n香港專案：<a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1396191c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\nFacebook： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhumanrightsfoundation%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=76b66b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/</a><br />\nInstagram： <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhrf%3Figshid%3D1s572yng420r8&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=0b83f1b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8</a><br />\nTwitter： @HRF（英文） @HRF_cn （中文）<br />\nTelegram： HRF或香港專案沒有tg channel，如有雷同實屬假冒，敬請report<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941049391a6e653545c8246b34e38bea2720979d","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"*Let&rsquo;s take complaints of human rights violation to a supranational forum! Hong Kong Desk of Human Rights Foundation*<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers and everyone who cares about Hong Kong, here is another way to help our beloved city! The Human Rights Foundation (HRF) is now setting up a HK desk to further combat human rights violations in HK.<br />\nOfficial landing page: <a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1396191c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\nLink to donate: <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f5ec1ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> (Currency: USD) (please use this link rather than the button on the official page - the button is for general donation and not dedicated to HK) <br />\n<br />\nHRF is a nonpartisan nonprofit organization that promotes and protects human rights globally, with a focus on closed societies. The proposed HK desk will: <br />\n- Bring China and HK government&rsquo;s suppression of liberties to a supranational level: File petitions and urgent appeals to 6 of the UN Human Rights&rsquo; Council Special Procedures<br />\n- Produce research reports and use media advocacy to maintain international attention on the subject<br />\n- Advocacy to hold perpetrators of human rights abuse in Hong Kong accountable<br />\n<br />\nUS$195,000 would sustain the project for an entire year. Please donate via <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f5ec1ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a>, and thank you for support against tyranny!<br />\n<br />\nPlease follow: <br />\nOfficial website - <a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=6c9aa54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://HRF.org</a><br />\nHong Kong Desk - <a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1396191c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\nFacebook-  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhumanrightsfoundation%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=76b66b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/</a><br />\nInstagram- <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhrf%3Figshid%3D1s572yng420r8&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=0b83f1b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8</a><br />\nTwitter- @HRF and @HRF_cn<br />\nTelegram- No official Telegram channel managed by HRF"},{"pid":"0bff6efa5e6bbd9d6be7766f2b75655779e41e35","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">常見問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成日吹緊海牙法庭，有冇得告?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好可惜暫時冇一個海牙法庭可以處理到香港情況，無論係International Criminal Court, International Court of Justice又或者最近好多人談論嘅Permanent Court of Arbitration，都係幫唔到香港。因為一係唔係member根本入唔到，一係唔啱嗰個法庭處理嘅事。而且，北韓新彊都未排到告上去，大家都唔想香港變到嗰個程度。現階段，呢個香港專案會專注聯合國戰線同國際文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><strong>聯合國真係有用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有，但將會係漫長嘅國際線，要逐份報告呈交上去，每一個相關committee都要寫，而且格式同程序都未必一樣。聯合國收到告狀，就會請中國回應，無論中國是否回應都會記喺每年嘅人權報告入面。當侵犯人權證據確鑿，就有更多國家向中共施壓喇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，記得之前何韻詩上UN講香港嗎？敵人即刻要搵兩個藍絲上去「正視聽」，證明其實中共港共都相當緊張喺聯合國入面嘅形象同地位㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解HRF唔用自己錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢哋一直有用一部分嘅經費嚟支持香港，就算今次籌唔夠錢都會繼續做，不過就冇辦法專題咁做了⋯一年嘅大project需要額外經費支持，佢哋都應承咗俾更多嘅人力物力出嚟。手足們，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔捐俾香港本土組織做呢件事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHRF嘅經驗同國際接觸同香港組織定位唔同，而且HRF喺全球對抗暴政已經有相當知名度，亦有成功以國際法或媒體推廣手段爭取釋放政治犯。同香港本土組織路線唔同，課金當然係多多益善唔止捐一個㗎嘛！雙管齊下，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔係官網捐錢而要用另一個籌款平台?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n技術上同管理上用平台做專題project籌款係方便好多，官網捐款無法指定用落香港度。Funraise呢個籌款平台係非牟利機構專用，大家可以放心啲錢係絕對會去咗HRF香港專題度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我之前見過私底下籌款，而家變咗公開眾籌嘅?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前的確有班善長仁翁預先支持咗一部分，令香港專案有經費可以正式開始，不過金額未達標，希望可以借群眾力量多多支持，籌夠錢可以長期作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有冇另一個捐錢方法例如銀行入數?</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請直接聯絡HRF。任何其他渠道取得的捐款都會計算在捐款總額內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲錢係咪一定會用喺香港專案?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定！HRF本身係美國註冊非牟利組織，每年都要通過審計先可以延續非牟利組織地位，所以數目要非常清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捐款可唔可以扣稅? </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHRF係美國501c3非牟利組織，可以扣美國稅。"},{"pid":"3eaaa9221e8106e6350b428d66eced0531cb3f29","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"1/100"},{"pid":"312c899e3b2b7f60362311882b82b9a473d38431","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"2/100"},{"pid":"5736ccb77cca9f6a52cd0a5e45e92aac8013ec41","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:24.000Z","msg":"3/100"},{"pid":"ba1597f81e9295aeaf9a7ed2380f1619d8cd4fb6","tid":1745472,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"a60b0328721f807e62e5cfb1b9dfc4aba29830a8","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"4/100"},{"pid":"61e2014f755d2f50c6e197dfef7393ff002190c2","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"5/100"},{"pid":"e00f107ce83a12c790476482a80ba9b4265b0e7d","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:10.000Z","msg":"6/100"},{"pid":"a20fed98e1a55b68dfdc8f09d857db4ea3f5542e","tid":1745472,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e849418e7894e5c40e721c66fdd48350c693bc3","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"7/100"},{"pid":"bf3d5718f1c8dfb4f3ab80a94ff5470d87575f67","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"8/100"},{"pid":"6be2f4019ba4ae9cf5dc328f734bd1a175197712","tid":1745472,"uid":116497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"9/100"},{"pid":"69f6c72af066e9691e50f61b4d4a461456508f87","tid":